subject: Automobile Racing
Autism
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson nosed past Tony Stewart with two laps left in a thrilling battle to the finish and won the Autism Speaks 400 at Dover International Speedway.
